---
// src/components/sections/Hero.astro
---

<section
    class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
    <!-- Background Image with Overlay -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566073771259-6a8506099945?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80"
            alt="Fascada del complejo turístico histórico"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
            fetchpriority="high"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-blue/40 mix-blend-multiply"></div>
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-brand-blue/80 via-transparent to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div
        class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-16"
    >
        <span
            class="block text-brand-gold font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm md:text-base mb-4 animate-fade-in-up"
        >
            Recuperando Espacios Atemporales
        </span>
        <h1
            class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold font-playfair text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-lg leading-tight animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-150"
        >
            Respira Nueva Vida en<br />Residencias de Herencia
        </h1>
        <p
            class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light drop-shadow-md animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-300"
        >
            Donde la historia se encuentra con el confort moderno. Redefinimos
            el significado del lujo clásico para tu descanso inolvidable.
        </p>

        <div class="animate-fade-in-up animation-delay-450">
            <a
                href="#alojamiento"
                class="inline-block bg-white text-brand-blue font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-sm hover:bg-brand-gold hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
                Descubrir Habitaciones
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 z-10 animate-bounce"
    >
        <a
            href="#about"
            class="text-white/70 hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors"
            aria-label="Scroll down"
        >
            <svg
                class="w-6 h-6"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg
            >
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Optional: Simple inline animations if tailwind config isn't extended yet */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }
    .animate-fade-in-up {
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        opacity: 0;
    }
    .animation-delay-150 {
        animation-delay: 150ms;
    }
    .animation-delay-300 {
        animation-delay: 300ms;
    }
    .animation-delay-450 {
        animation-delay: 450ms;
    }
</style>
